channel.title: Things to merchant
channel.description:
Im new here so ill post some things good i merchant
Vials buy in shops or at herblore store and fill them with water and offer them on a forums for 150 ea
Other ways to start of do Death plateau quest and buy climb boots 12gp ea sell for 2-5k ea
Fury ammys buy 4.8m-4.9m and sell 5m-5.1m
Green d hides Go to a low persons world edgeville,varrok east bank say buying green d hide 1.3k ea sell 1.5-1.6k ea in fally world 2 beside bank
Rune is a good thing to merchant W2 beside fence buy rune legs for 30-35k ea rune plates 50k ea rune kites 40k ea scims 20k ea helms 15k ea head world 1 varrok and sell full sets 190-200k ea
Bank sales are a good way to make money usually they have good stuff and will sell for a lower price
D chains price 2 buy 15.5-15.7 Sell anywhere over 15.8
Obby capes Price 2 buy 240k price 2 sell 260k-270k
Obby sheilds price to buy 280k-290k Sell 300k+
Rune Boots Price to buy 180k-190k Sell 200k
In world 2 things go for pretty cheap d long 80k,Mauls 50k etc look for them
Zammy pages Page 1 200k-220k Page 2 200k-220k Page 3 200k-220k Page 4 200k-220k Sell all pages 250k ea
Cannons Buy 500k ea Sell 550 ea
Sharks Buy 800 ea sell 900-950 ea
Lobs Buy 200 ea Sell 250 ea
Will update this when i think of more
